krunner-lechat (0.4~beta1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Version 0.4 (Beta) release
  * Uses system python3-markdown instead of venv for better distribution support.
  * Full markdown rendering support (tables, code blocks, lists).
  * Web search enabled by default via Mistral API agents.
  * Multiple trigger keywords: katten, lechat, lc, mistral, vibe, mv.
  * Preview panel with KDE Plasma integration.
  * Auto-start on session login.
  * Rebranded from Le Chat to Vibe.

 -- Emilio Longoria <hej@emilio.dk>  Sat, 06 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
